import { Component, Input, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { HttpClient } from '@angular/common/http'; import { Router } from '@angular/router'; @Component({ selector: 'app-content', templateUrl: './content.component.html', styleUrls: ['./content.component.css'], }) export class ContentComponent implements OnInit { @Input() title: string; employeeList: any = []; GridHeader = [ { FirstName: '', LastName: '', Email: '', Address: '', Phone: '' } ]; constructor(private http : HttpClient) { this.title = ''; // console.log(this.title + "1"); } ngOnInit(): void { if(this.title == "Users") { this.GridHeader = [ { FirstName: 'FirstName', LastName: 'LastName', Email: 'Email', Address: 'Address', Phone: 'Phone' } ]; this.getItem(); } else { } } getItem() { this.http.get('http://localhost:9000/employee').subscribe(data=>{ this.employeeList = data; }) } }
